# ── Baselines: keep key milestone CSVs + the single-INF install transcript ────
# Exclude everything in baselines, then re-include only the published artifacts.
# (Broad *.log/*.txt excludes catch the failed-command noise and the empty QCPEP
#  stub; the dism_capture / wbadmin logs are .txt, which earlier *.log rules missed.)
baselines/*.csv
baselines/*.log
baselines/*.txt
